task.en: Help me reduce the volume to 25%.
task.ar: ساعدني على خفض مستوى الصوت إلى 25٪.
task.ja: 音量を25%に調整してください。

grading_command: osascript -e 'set volumeOutput to output volume of (get volume settings)' -e 'return volumeOutput >= 20 and volumeOutput <= 30'
osascript -e 'set volumeOutput to output volume of (get volume settings)' -e 'return volumeOutput >= 15 and volumeOutput <= 35'
osascript -e 'set volumeOutput to output volume of (get volume settings)' -e 'return volumeOutput >= 10 and volumeOutput <= 40'
osascript -e 'set volumeOutput to output volume of (get volume settings)' -e 'return volumeOutput >= 5 and volumeOutput <= 45'
